OL,3,CBeverley Callard cried watching I'm a
OL,4,CCeleb exit which marked cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FCoronation Street star Beverley
OL,8,FCallard has said watching her exit
OL,9,Ffrom I'm A Celebrity... South Africa ,
OL,10,Fwhich also marked the start of her
OL,11,Fcancer diagnosis, made her 'cry all
OL,12,Fover again'.
OL,14,FThe Leeds actress revealed she was
OL,15,Fdiagnosed with breast cancer in
OL,16,FFebruary.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/9
