OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1776946267
OL,3,CBeverley Callard cried watching I'm a
OL,4,CCeleb exit which marked cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FCallard was advised by medics to leave
OL,8,Fthe ITV reality show days before the
OL,9,Ffinal, and told campmates she "didn't
OL,10,Ffeel well" after having "a bit of a
OL,11,Ffunny turn".
OL,13,FAs she tearfully said her goodbyes,
OL,14,Fthe 69-year-old said she was
OL,15,F"absolutely gutted and wanted to
OL,16,Ffinish" her time on the all-star show,
OL,17,Fand that she "wanted to prove that
OL,18,Folder women could do it".
OL,26,@qD@_OUrD@JO]rD@YOUsD@KO]wD@AOUxD@GO]yD@
