OL,3,CBeverley Callard cried watching I'm a
OL,4,CCeleb exit which marked cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FThe actress, who revealed she was
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with breast cancer in
OL,9,FFebruary, shared her emotional
OL,10,Freaction to her departure in a video
OL,11,Fshared to Instagram on Tuesday night,
OL,12,F21 April.
OL,14,FShe said: "Well, I've just watched my
OL,15,Fexit on I'm A Celeb, and it made me
OL,16,Fcry all over again because, of course,
OL,17,FI didn't know then that I had cancer,
OL,18,Fbut I just knew that the last couple
OL,19,Fof days there I had not felt very well.
OL,26,@vD@KOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
