OL,3,CBeverley Callard cried watching I'm a
OL,4,CCeleb exit which marked cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,F"What happened was I was called into
OL,8,Fthe Bush Telegraph, and apparently I
OL,9,Flost consciousness for a little while
OL,10,Fand I went yonder-ly, as they say, and
OL,11,FI just wasn't feeling myself.
OL,13,F"They took me to a medical hut, they
OL,14,Fwere amazing. They really looked after
OL,15,Fme. And then they said, 'You can't go
OL,16,Fback'.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
