OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1776946267
OL,3,CBeverley Callard cried watching I'm a
OL,4,CCeleb exit which marked cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,F"And I said, 'Don't send me home, I'm
OL,8,Fsure I'll be fine', you know, I had
OL,9,Fjumped out of a plane, hung off a
OL,10,Fcliff, and I did want to succeed and
OL,11,Fmake it through to the end.
OL,13,F"But that was the start of everything,
OL,14,Freally. So it's made me really
OL,15,Femotional. But I will beat this. I
OL,16,Fwill beat it."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUxD@NO]
