OL,3,CBeverley Callard cried watching I'm a
OL,4,CCeleb exit which marked cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FBeneath the post Callard, best known
OL,8,Ffor her role as Liz McDonald in
OL,9,FCoronation Street, wrote: "That was
OL,10,Fsuch an emotional watch... especially
OL,11,Fknowing what I know now.
OL,13,F"I wanted to prove that age is just a
OL,14,Fnumber and I feel so proud of what I
OL,15,Fachieved. Just got to get through this
OL,16,Freal life trial now _imaceleb."
OL,26,@qD@[OUuD@AOUxD@_O]
