OL,3,CBeverley Callard cried watching I'm a
OL,4,CCeleb exit which marked cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FSince announcing her diagnosis of
OL,8,Fearly-stage breast cancer in February,
OL,9,Fthe actress has documented her
OL,10,Ftreatment on her Instagram and has
OL,11,Frecently undergone surgery to remove
OL,12,Fthe cancer.
OL,14,FCallard's comments were flooded with
OL,15,Fsupport from fans and fellow
OL,16,Fcelebrities including I'm A Celeb co-
OL,17,Fstar Ashley Roberts, who wrote: "You
OL,18,Fdid prove that Bev. Sending love and
OL,19,Fso proud of you."
OL,26,@yD@aOU{D@QO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
