OL,3,CBeverley Callard cried watching I'm a
OL,4,CCeleb exit which marked cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FSinger Coleen Nolan said "so proud of
OL,8,Fyou Bev" followed by a heart emoji,
OL,9,Fand comedian Jon Richardson commented:
OL,10,F"Sending love Beverley."
OL,12,FOther celebrities to offer their
OL,13,Fsupport include Emmerdale actress
OL,14,FHayley Soraya Tamaddon and socialite
OL,15,FLizzie Cundy.
